```

## Event Object

```javascript
document.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
  // Temel bilgiler
  console.log(event.type);       // "click"
  console.log(event.target);     // TÄ±klanan element
  console.log(event.currentTarget); // Listener'Ä±n baÄŸlÄ± olduÄŸu element

  // Pozisyon (mouse events)
  console.log(event.clientX, event.clientY); // Viewport'a gÃ¶re
